rows.label: qst200604_0010
rows.name:
Demon or no, 'twas a mere beast.
It could not hope to rival a king.

rows.label: qst200604_0020
rows.name: We beat it...

rows.label: qst200604_0030
rows.name: Yeah. We actually beat it.

rows.label: qst200604_0040
rows.name:
I gotta say, I didn't think we'd
actually do it.

rows.label: qst200604_0050
rows.name:
Honestly...
Have you no pride?!

rows.label: qst200604_0060
rows.name:
How could we fail to overcome
such a trifling foe?

rows.label: qst200604_0070
rows.name:
Frankly, you should be ashamed
that you did not slay it more swiftly.

rows.label: qst200604_0080
rows.name: Uh, right...

rows.label: qst200604_0090
rows.name:
I gotta say, though... You're pretty
awesome when you go all out, Kubira.

rows.label: qst200604_0100
rows.name:
Indeed. I knew you were hiding your full strength,
but this was more than I had bargained for.

rows.label: qst200604_0110
rows.name:
I'm glad we met you as an
ally, not an enemy.

rows.label: qst200604_0120
rows.name: Are you still thinking about your lost kingdom?

rows.label: qst200604_0130
rows.name: It is as you see.

rows.label: qst200604_0140
rows.name:
For one so great as I, to slay
such a foe is a simple task.

rows.label: qst200604_0150
rows.name:
And yet... Though the beast lies
defeated, the kingdom remains lost.

rows.label: qst200604_0160
rows.name:
There is no way for us to be certain
it was even the land I once ruled.

rows.label: qst200604_0170
rows.name: Kubira...

rows.label: qst200604_0180
rows.name: Hey, don't be such a downer.

rows.label: qst200604_0190
rows.name:
No point worrying about what's dead and gone.
If you want a kingdom, you should make a new one!

rows.label: qst200604_0200
rows.name: Yeah, Zeke's right.

rows.label: qst200604_0210
rows.name:
If you try your hardest,
anything's possible!

rows.label: qst200604_0220
rows.name:
Interesting...
There is a certain wisdom in your counsel.

rows.label: qst200604_0230
rows.name: Now that my nemesis lies slain...

rows.label: qst200604_0240
rows.name:
It is not fitting for a king to
dwell forever on the past.

rows.label: qst200604_0250
rows.name: My path of conquest is far from over!

rows.label: qst200604_0260
rows.name:
I am the man who will someday rule
this entire world!

rows.label: qst200604_0270
rows.name:
Hahahahahah! Hahahahahah!
Hahahahahah!

rows.label: qst200604_0280
rows.name: Well, he certainly seems motivated now...

rows.label: qst200604_0290
rows.name:
Kubira have energy, but still
not quite in touch with reality.

rows.label: qst200604_0300
rows.name:
Hear this. You have yet to prove your might as retainers.
Therefore, I will lend you my royal strength.

rows.label: qst200604_0310
rows.name: However, 'tis only for the sake of my righteous victory!

rows.label: qst200604_0320
rows.name: Never forget this, my subjects!

rows.label: qst200604_0330
rows.name:
Hahahahahah! Hahahahahah!
Hahahahahah!

rows.label: qst200604_0340
rows.name:
It's great that he's getting
into this, and all...

rows.label: qst200604_0350
rows.name: But his attitude still bugs me.

rows.label: qst200604_0360
rows.name: Don't be too harsh.

rows.label: qst200604_0370
rows.name:
For all his words, I do believe he
cares for us. Let's be happy for him.

rows.label: qst200604_0380
rows.name: Sounds about right.

rows.label: qst200604_0390
rows.name:
Being able to deal even with total nutters like him
is the mark of a real Driver!

rows.label: qst200604_0400
rows.name: If you say so...

rows.label: qst200604_0410
rows.name:
Haha... Hahahahahah!
Hahahahahahahahah!
